6_Experiments._text:
This section provides a detailed empirical analysis of SPIN. Our findings highlight several key points: (1) SPIN markedly enhances model performance across a wide range of evaluation benchmarks by breaking the limit of SFT;
(2) even without introducing new human annotated data, SPIN at iteration 0 achieves performance on par to DPO training that utilizes even more data;
(3) iterative training is a necessary component in SPIN as it breaks the limit of multi-epoch training.
